Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway sit down to talk about the newest Hunter Biden investigation, Jemele Hill accusing Jake Paul of being racist for knocking out Nate Robinson during a sanctioned boxing event, an Israeli general’s claim that aliens are real and in contact with Earth (and whether or not Trump will straight up tell everyone on his way out), plus the new bipartisan anti-trust suit against Facebook and Colin Kaepernick’s new Ben & Jerry’s flavor.
